snippet: Brassard did not return to practice, but Coach Alain Vigneault said he expected him to be available when the Rangers open their playoff series Thursday against the Flyers.
lead_paragraph: Brassard did not return to practice, but Coach Alain Vigneault said he expected him to be available when the Rangers open their playoff series Thursday against the Flyers.
